15 have experience in completing farm transfers.
16 (2) The Secretary of Agriculture, Food and Markets shall make the
17 toolkit available on the Agency of Agriculture, Food and Markets’ website to
18 any person who requests the toolkit.
19 (c) As part of the Program, the Secretary shall conduct at least three
20 educational workshops a year for the purpose of connecting owners of
