13 telecommunications, and video- or audio-conferencing conference telephone
14 call, by which all members participating may simultaneously or sequentially
15 communicate with each other during the meeting. A member participating in a
16 meeting by this means is deemed to be present in person at the meeting.
17 (g) Compensation. Private sector members shall be entitled to per diem
